  {
    "lat": -3107.808692326502,
    "lng": 5243.310612591347,
    "title": "Serial Killer Scrawlings",
    "icon": "easter_egg",
    "popupHtml": "<div class=\"p-1\">\n  <div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 mb-2\">\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white leading-tight\">Serial Killer Scrawlings</h3>\n    <button class=\"copy p-1.5 bg-gray-700/50 hover:bg-blue-500 text-gray-400 hover:text-white rounded transition-colors\" data-clipboard-text=\"-3107.808692326502, 5243.310612591347\" title=\"Copy Location\">\n      <svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M8 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-1M8 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M8 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 0h2a2 2 0 012 2v3m2 4H10m0 0l3-3m-3 3l3 3\" /></svg>\n    </button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3\">Several '8's and a sinister rhyme can be found on a large rock here.\n\n*One is done*\n\n_Two was fun_\n\n_Three tried to run_\n\n_Four called mom_\n\n_Fives not alive_\n\n_Six is nix_\n\n_Seven's in heaven_\n\n_8 won't wait_</p>\n</div>"
