  {
    "lat": -1808.4780371473717,
    "lng": 5756.385615547488,
    "title": "Jolene Cranley-Evans's Ghost",
    "icon": "easter_egg",
    "popupHtml": "<div class=\"p-1\">\n  <div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 mb-2\">\n    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white leading-tight\">Jolene Cranley-Evans's Ghost</h3>\n    <button class=\"copy p-1.5 bg-gray-700/50 hover:bg-blue-500 text-gray-400 hover:text-white rounded transition-colors\" data-clipboard-text=\"-1808.4780371473717, 5756.385615547488\" title=\"Copy Location\">\n      <svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M8 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-1M8 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M8 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 0h2a2 2 0 012 2v3m2 4H10m0 0l3-3m-3 3l3 3\" /></svg>\n    </button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3\">Travel to the marker above between 23:00 and 24:00 (11:00 PM / 12:00 Midnight) to see a ghostly image appear and a bloody message written on the Mt. Gordo peak.\n\nThe message reads “Jock” which happens to be the first name of Jock Cranley, the Vinewood Stuntman turned Conservative candidate for Governor.\n\nYouTube Video Below (http://youtu.be/HMj8jrTgeuk)</p>\n</div>"
  },
